# Performance Metrics

The optimized GAAFET was evaluated using standard semiconductor device metrics.

| Metric | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| ION | ON-state drain current |
| IOFF | OFF-state leakage current |
| ION/IOFF | Current switching capability |
| VTH | Threshold voltage |
| SS | Subthreshold swing |
| Leakage Current | Static power consumption |

## Key Improvements

- Lower OFF-state leakage
- Improved gate control
- Higher ON/OFF current ratio
- Enhanced switching characteristics
- Suitable for low-power logic applications
